{"type": "article", "id": 59267, "title": "蔡徐坤成为宝格丽品牌挚友，  Uber 超大型玩具车免费乘坐 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-13T05:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 566, "name": "手机"}, {"id": 34647, "name": "宝格丽"}, {"id": 1520, "name": "Uber"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/201812131153294cNLrM7OYAZt0W2y.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"SYmp\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2090537982/4316365063980962\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>蔡徐坤成为宝格丽品牌挚友。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114515HierGKp23jlM4XP8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p line=\"PGYi\">从 12 月 10 日开始，华为每天公布一支 nova4 的广告短片，意在展示刘海屏被极点取代。</p><p line=\"CIrB\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4315680897674481?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>天台上猫咪吓跑了小麻雀</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u0810t6p9q1\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Z6yj\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4315996510714139?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>快速清理泳池的秘诀</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d081191nymk\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"823e\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4315680897674481?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>来变个魔术</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r08118k25cm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"fKFo\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MjAwOTM0MA==&amp;mid=2651126458&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=80678e5658746f0d07e214b7b09397d0&amp;chksm=bd5c87a98a2b0ebfbe5c94b95be4fa97e527a9a4d2e0b00718a00cf885b501d6f4392a1aa445&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1213ING0B6wh3PK2Ir0DYOnB&amp;key=b97634afb8bc8a87846abfb5740e0ff84f779c69474fa140b3068dda4c8ecdeda73914a3580fdbe39c1854ce2efe067ef209a5ba3bdff71d99a1564b2ecd7388b27a874d0e2972837c3dc318dd13227b&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=Qp3MyuwpqniczT%2F50VZFWmyhcrBVFQreHiqjO0rA9NKMQ15VpGRwzebJ%2FYR7LA%2Bz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">搜狗输入法联合北冰洋发布了“北京话 2018 大考” H5</a>，</b>借此小游戏来宣传搜狗输入法的方言词库。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114637Mzv7jU4LdBFcC5uf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.779940\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114637QVxiEvpFIOdW2q0e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.717333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"DB7a\">钉钉的吉祥物“钉三多”去北京建国门地铁站上了一堂<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4316004672973079\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“职场残酷真相课”</b></a>，把职场上大家遇到的沟通难题，制作成了巨幅海报，配上职场人平时想说不敢说的内心想法，出现在上班族聚集的地铁站里。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018121311470056SgF8Kqap2vBnPd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114700exydT3s05U7Qf4n8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114701jT5mB7A6RFDrUg1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114701FWqkzIEY0BTlNndh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114701OYGEKP2WL5BNT4Zn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.462500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"M8Vf\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU3MjU2ODIwNw==&amp;mid=2247484426&amp;idx=4&amp;sn=680481cb8ab1de3907e9cafab39919c8&amp;chksm=fccfa3eacbb82afc0fd876fb13a254276741cbea4b32b222044de6b6b77852bac0990c736be6&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=12135OMJjWtlHrUoWPBfanMD&amp;key=424e54978849d9561945c7fe1b3abdff5994dd178c79d169d4aa18caeb62ca848dfb0eb67c201d84c7597f625534b5d7fe2611d2d7a7cfdba4aa9649598b72c49b2860d273a382d4809bdc5c24cd0b52&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=Qp3MyuwpqniczT%2F50VZFWmyhcrBVFQreHiqjO0rA9NKMQ15VpGRwzebJ%2FYR7LA%2Bz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>安踏即将和 NASA 合作在广州打造“超重力空间站”，</b></a>这次活动是为了选出安踏新款“A-FLASH 虫洞鞋”。在现场的参观者将可以穿着新款鞋子，体验超重力下的回弹力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181213114716Hw1JUrsx8GjpIqY7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470313\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"b7EQ\">江南布衣旗下的环保时尚品牌 REVERB 拍摄了一支广告<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/6572640578/4315798392700566\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“证明未来”</b></a>，将其循环再生的过程通过男女主人公的表演展现出来。由 Nowness 制作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0810p8pah8\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"zT4Y\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YM58p90uZos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Uber 在欧洲推出“优步玩具”（Uber Toys）的免费乘车计划，</b></a>在巴黎将会有 6 种不同的超大型玩具车可以承载，包括乐高建筑砖车和遥控汽车。接下来 Uber 还会去到苏黎世和维也纳。代理商是 DDB 巴黎。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0812tkg9ly\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"OmgC\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/bIDnCvxvnmo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>一系列动物福利组织希望人们能够在节假日期间收养在收容所的狗狗们，</b></a>广告来自 DDB Remedy。此外，片中，狗狗的画外音是由“复仇者联盟2”中快银的扮演者 Aaron Taylor-Johnson 配音。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=p08122i2q4s\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"1U5W\"><b><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/12/12/lidl-names-karmarama-lead-uk-creative-agency-following-tbwa-split\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lidl 的新代理商换成了 Karmarama&nbsp;</a>，后者</b>将于明年 3 月接替已经合作了 5 年的 TBWA，为埃森哲所有的店铺制定新的长期品牌战略。</p><p line=\"1U5W\"><br></p><p line=\"1U5W\" class=\"\">题图来自：Unsplash@<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@lh1me\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">HONG LIN</a></p>"}